<plot>Christianity began with a miracle-the virgin birth of the Son of God-and the earliest days of Christ's existence were suffered with a power that reaches across millennia to touch us today. Hosted by Roger Moore, In the Footsteps of the Holy Family traces the journey of Jesus, Mary and Joseph after Christ's birth, visiting the sites made sacred by their presence.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?263059</url></doc>
